@startuml Admin Verify Coach Profile
!theme plain
title Admin Verify Coach Profile - Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Admin Portal" as Portal
participant "Backend" as API
participant "Coach Service" as CoachService
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

== Admin View Pending Coaches ==
Admin -> Portal: Navigate to Coach Management
activate Portal
Portal -> API: GET /coaches?filter=verificationStatus=PENDING
activate API
API -> DB: Query Coaches WHERE verificationStatus = UNVERIFIED/PENDING
activate DB
DB --> API: Return List of Coaches
deactivate DB
API --> Portal: Return Coaches List
deactivate API
Portal --> Admin: Display Pending Coach Profiles

== Admin Review Coach Profile ==
Admin -> Portal: Click on Coach Profile to Review
activate Admin
Portal -> API: GET /coaches/:coachId
activate API
API -> DB: Query Coach with Relations\n(user, credentials, created courses)
activate DB
DB --> API: Return Coach Details\n(bio, yearOfExperience, specialties,\ncredentials[], courses[])
deactivate DB
API --> Portal: Coach Full Profile
deactivate API
Portal --> Admin: Display Coach Details\n- Profile Info\n- Uploaded Credentials\n- Years of Experience\n- Specialties

== Admin Verification Decision ==

deactivate Admin

